.------------------------------------------
. Standard Variables Required for Screen 
.          Painting Routines
.------------------------------------------
REPSTR     DIM       4
FI40       FORM      "40"
NEWATTR    DIM       1
DIMCCOL    DIM       3
DIMCVERT   DIM       2
FARRAY    FORM      1[80][24]  * Flag Array for Moving Screen Information
CARRAY    DIM       1[80][24]  * Character Array for Moving Screen Information
AARRAY    DIM       1[80][24]  * Attributes Array for Moving Screen Information
VERT      FORM      2           * New Vertical Position for Move
VERTOFF   FORM      3           * Vertical Offset for Move
COLOFF    FORM      4           * Horizontal Offset for Move
LINETYPE  FORM      1           * Graphic Line Type 1 Single 2 Double 3 Erase
LLCNT     FORM      3           * Logical Length Counter
LINE      FORM      2           * Display Line
FV2LON    FORM      1           * Flag *V2LON   0 off 1 on
FHON      FORM      1           * Flag *HON     0 off 1 on
FULON     FORM      1           * Flag *ULON    0 off 1 on
FBLINK    FORM      1           * Flag *BLINKON 0 off 1 on
SCRNSAVE  FORM      1           * Flag to Check if Screen has been Changed
FLAG      FORM      1           * Video Load Flag
SCOL      FORM      3           * Save Column
SVERT     FORM      3           * Save Row
CDATA     DIM       1           * Single Character Get
CATTR     DIM       1           * Single Attribute Get
CDATA80   DIM       80          * Single Character Get
CATTR80   DIM       80          * Single Attribute Get
G         DIM       1[45]       * Graphic Character Array
GCHARNUM  FORM      2           * Graphic Character Array SUBSTRipt
GRAPHIC   DIM       45          * Load Variable for Graphics Character
GRAPATTB  DIM       45          * Load Variable for Graphics Attributes
MINLINE   FORM      2           * First Screen Line   Min 3
MAXLINE   FORM      2           * Last Line On Screen Max 24
MINCOL    FORM      3           * First Screen Column Min 1
MAXCOL    FORM      3           * Last Screen Column  Max 132
F132      FORM      "132"
SP80      INIT      "                                        ":
                    "                                        "
.
ATTNORM   EQU       0x00        * Normal Video
ATTHON    EQU       0x01        * Inverse Video
ATTV2LON  EQU       0x02        * Highlight Video
ATTULON   EQU       0x04        * Underline Video
ATTBLINK  EQU       0x08        * Blink Video
ATTGRAPH  EQU       0x20        * Graphic Video
.
AGRAPHIC  DIM       4[45]
SUBSTR    FORM      2
DIM3      DIM       3
DIM4      DIM       4
.
RLEF      DIM       1
RRIG      DIM       1
RTOP      DIM       1
RBOT      DIM       1
.
